cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "omni-docking-bench: A Reproducibility Benchmark for Precision Docking Controllers on a Double-Steering-Drive Omni AMR"
abstract: >-
  Reproducibility package for the ICROS 2026 paper on precision short-range
  docking of a double-steering-drive omni-directional AMR. Compares a kinematic
  convergence controller against Nav2 MPPI and DWB, using PGV100-F200A-R4
  optical marker feedback for a 3 mm settling criterion at a 3 cm start distance.
authors:
